pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1XYXRjaC1NaWRuaWdodC1BbHVtaW51bS1BbHdheXMvZHAvQjBCREhGNzU3Ri8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTk4LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI1NmQ5Zjg5ZC01YWY5LTQyN2EtYjE1Zi0xZTk5N2M1YWIwMGYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYPVPBsgPF8RZRiVovcn4E-Aq3AZ3hhM6fKXgbhOpmR5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Watch-Midnight-Aluminum-Always%2Fdp%2FB0BDHF757F%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Watch Series 8</a> ，Prime Day 为其提供 120 美元折扣。通常 399 美元，41 毫米 GPS 型号现在为 280 美元。 Series 8 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">最喜欢的智能手表</a>，因为它具有详细的健康和健身跟踪功能，以及与 iPhone 应用程序和通知的无缝集成。温度传感器、心电图和血氧读数以及改进的睡眠指标等新功能为您提供比以往更多的数据，而碰撞检测可以在您发生事故时寻求帮助。 <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">即将推出的 WatchOS 10</a>将添加小部件和扩展功能，包括在正念应用程序中跟踪您的心情的方法。</p><h2>苹果手表 SE </h2><p><core-commerce id="27dc535f038c40e5bd006062163a2ae4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFRRRFJaLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOTgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjU2ZDlmODlkLTVhZjktNDI3YS1iMTVmLTFlOTk3YzVhYjAwZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcN2CNpGpWlhxKeYOiUCmgomh7frnTHnSqIOO7scZuPM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHTQDRZ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Watch SE</a>是 Apple 的廉价智能手表，通常售价为 250 美元。 Prime Day 折扣使得 40 毫米尺寸的售价仅为 200 美元。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFFUMTFWP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAARl2Psgm_AsHjHzFj3jFzQ6zX41fqDf-__DmBlhwZPWB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHQT11V" class="rapid-with-clickid">44 毫米版本</a>通常售价 270 美元，但售价可降至 230 美元。我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-se-2022-review-battery-life-workout-health-tracking-144551799.html">Engadget 评论</a>中将 SE 称为“250 美元能买到的最好的智能手表”。令人惊讶的是，它与 Series 8 相比几乎没有做出任何牺牲，并且具有相同的外观、处理器和 50 米防水性能。它没有常亮显示屏，也没有血氧、体温和心电图读数传感器。如果您不需要所有这些，您仍然可以获得大量健身和健康数据以及与 iPhone 的无缝集成。</p><p>我们的评论员 Cherlynn Low 指出，苹果在 SE 上做出的牺牲少之又少，并称其为“性价比最好的智能手表”。事实上，在 Apple Watch 8 报道的总结中，她<a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-8-real-world-test-130031046.html">表示，</a>如果她为自己购物，SE 就是她会购买的手表。</p><p>蜂窝网络型号也在 Prime Day 期间发售。即使您的 iPhone 不在身边，GPS + 蜂窝网络型号也能让您接听电话、发短信和播放音乐。 Prime Day 起价为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESkxaWFZDP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAQZXFysLRj4DezCYRxWaNJeL4ivhQri-bd6mWYYUMxrJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDJLZXVC" class="rapid-with-clickid">249 美元</a>。</p><h2> MacBook Pro（M2，14 英寸） </h2><p><core-commerce id="202943c7a93641fc912c55177f6fd4b8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> MacBook Pro 的 M2 Pro 和 M2 Max 芯片为音乐制作人、视频制作人和其他重度用户提供了大量的处理能力。亚马逊正在以 1,799 美元的价格出售配备 M2 Pro 芯片、16GB 内存和 512GB 存储空间的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJTSERWQlhaLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOTgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjU2ZDlmODlkLTVhZjktNDI3YS1iMTVmLTFlOTk3YzVhYjAwZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcNiUeInGE1JG1BbiyAWVOU9wzdGpwlQYXdYsuQzc5Tc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BSHDVBXZ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">14 英寸 MacBook Pro</a>基本型号，比平时的 1,999 美元便宜了 200 美元。具有相同规格的基本型号<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJTSEY3TExMLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOTgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjU2ZDlmODlkLTVhZjktNDI3YS1iMTVmLTFlOTk3YzVhYjAwZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAaSv2XWzHEHM25OMfe0sv46ux7VrSqpOqv1tSz7U3pT5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BSHF7LLL%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">16 英寸 MacBook Pro</a>价格从 2,499 美元降至 2,299 美元。当新款 MacBook Pro 在今年 1 月推出时，我们给这款 14 英寸型号的<a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-pro-14-inch-review-2023-m2-pro-max-140048268.html">评分为 92 分</a>，称赞其 Liquid Retina XDR 显示屏、坚固的设计和丰富的端口，包括三个 Thunderbolt 4 USB-C、HDMI、一个耳机插孔和全尺寸 SD 卡插槽。</p><p> 2022 款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIzQzU3WExSLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOTgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjU2ZDlmODlkLTVhZjktNDI3YS1iMTVmLTFlOTk3YzVhYjAwZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARDIuC2SDCJdTNNpqDN0aWPFspzue9kuN_iLC_n16pbp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B3C57XLR%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">13 英寸 MacBook Pro</a>折扣 200 美元后，售价为 1,099 美元，但我们对这款机器的<a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/macbook-pro-13-inch-review-m2-2022-130005000.html">印象并不深刻</a>。如果您对 13 英寸屏幕感到满意，那么您最好选择<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:40;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIzQzJSOE1QP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAfxfqxMnKqRDqUo7awjXmgn496bZqQ_5vuXrKznfd72r&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B3C2R8MP" class="rapid-with-clickid">13 英寸 MacBook Air</a> 。</p><h2> AirPods Max </h2><p><core-commerce id="8fa6d18066884219afa90fb3fdc38fba" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果的头戴式耳机<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:41;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yah