 cameras including 1080p video recordings and support for two-way talk and motion alerts.</p><p> <strong><em>Your Prime Day Shopping Guide</em></strong> <em>: See all of our</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day</em></a> <em>coverage.</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳科技优惠</em></a><em>。 Learn about</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/tag/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day trends</em></a> <em>on In the Know. Hear from Autoblog&#39;s car experts on must-shop auto-related</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:65;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/article/amazon-prime-day-2023/"><em>Prime Day deals</em></a> <em>and find</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:66;pos:1" href="https://www.aol.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-day-090057255.html"><em>Prime Day sales</em></a> <em>to shop on AOL, handpicked just for you.</em></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-2023-120012352.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-2023-120012352.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aadd0596-160b-4ee2-b204-8136aab9ce63</guid><dc:creator>恩杰特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 13:10:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689081017</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T13:10:49+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider