Zi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFRRRFJaLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xb2ktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjIyYzU5MmUxLTA0YzUtNGQ1ZC04MjNmLWY0MzcxYmM2YTQ1OCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAYpjMv7f_ZxJRFBR8rui3R7gNSvNuLLfxaS_GOzex8CM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHTQDRZ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Watch SE</a> . Options from other brands like Samsung and Fitbit are also on sale. We&#39;ve rounded up some of our recommended fitness trackers that are getting Prime Day discounts as well. Here are the best Prime Day deals on Apple Watches we could find.</p><h2> Apple Watch Series 8 </h2><p><core-commerce id="251c1231cdb942e7ace4e5bddbeed5e5" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1XYXRjaC1NaWRuaWdodC1BbHVtaW51bS1BbHdheXMvZHAvQjBCREhGNzU3Ri8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMW9pLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmM1OTJlMS0wNGM1LTRkNWQtODIzZi1mNDM3MWJjNmE0NTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAUlIudVfwHfhrL77kl8GldOdTgwHlD49XtNUQxUM0GQq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Watch-Midnight-Aluminum-Always%2Fdp%2FB0BDHF757F%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Watch Series 8</a> is the brand&#39;s most recent flagship and usually sells for $399 for the 41mm GPS model. Prime Day brings it down to $280, which is the best price we&#39;ve seen. The Series 8 is our top pick <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">in our guide</a> to smartwatches because it combines detailed health and fitness tracking with seamless iPhone integration. New features include temperature sensors, ECG and blood oxygen readings, crash detection, and improved sleep metrics. The <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">upcoming WatchOS 10</a> will bump the utility even more with widgets plus expanded health, fitness and mindfulness features.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> We <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-8-real-world-test-130031046.html">spent some time</a> with the Apple Watch 8 when it came out late last year and called it “well-rounded [and] fully featured.” Apple claims an 18-hour battery life with average use and the always-on display enabled. Low-power mode (which we found particularly impressive) can give you up to 36 hours. If you want to make calls, get texts and more when you don&#39;t have your phone, you may want to get the model with cellular capabilities. Those versions are down to <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESjFNWU1XL3JlZj1mc19hX3d0Ml91czE_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMW9pLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmM1OTJlMS0wNGM1LTRkNWQtODIzZi1mNDM3MWJjNmE0NTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAfFaAcUcw3bS7bPeW65pTFFoPmPysDbXyMQJEsqRjGxh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDJ1MYMW%2Fref%3Dfs_a_wt2_us1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BDJ1MYMW/ref=fs_a_wt2_us1?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">$380</a> for both case sizes.</p><h2> Apple Watch SE </h2><p><core-commerce id="420bf95e2f154082a4d4fd691efd0da2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The most affordable smartwatch in the lineup is the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFRRRFJaLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xb2ktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjIyYzU5MmUxLTA0YzUtNGQ1ZC04MjNmLWY0MzcxYmM2YTQ1OCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAYpjMv7f_ZxJRFBR8rui3R7gNSvNuLLfxaS_GOzex8CM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHTQDRZ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Watch SE</a> . Usually $250, Prime Day discounts are making it just $200 for the 40 mm size. The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFFUMTFWP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJjNTkyZTEtMDRjNS00ZDVkLTgyM2YtZjQzNzFiYzZhNDU4In0&amp;signature=AQAAATK3U40xAeM4_T9DjJa7rzbrKlRPcbUpIXr-03jzAhNj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHQT11V" class="rapid-with-clickid">44mm version</a> is usually $270 but down to $230 for the sale. We called the SE “the best smartwatch $250 can buy” in our <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-se-2022-review-battery-life-workout-health-tracking-144551799.html">Engadget review</a> . It uses the same processor, matches the 50 meter water resistance and looks nearly identical to the Apple Watch 8, though the SE lacks dust resistance and the always-on display. It also can&#39;t give blood oxygen, temperature and EKG readings. But if you don&#39;t need those things, you can save money while still getting plenty of fitness and health data along with seamless integration with your iPhone.</p><h2> Smartwatches from other brands</h2><h2>三星 Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="19653fd9fa1a4006bdcb5bd247a4f1e3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Of course, Apple Watches only work with iPhones. For those who prefer Android devices, the <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQjJKNVRCM1E_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMW9pLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmM1OTJlMS0wNGM1LTRkNWQtODIzZi1mNDM3MWJjNmE0NTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVETYTaDZwUx3oydrtYiA_SnQzNN9KsOxWtEgPrDZHBx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B2J5TB3Q" class="rapid-with-clickid">Galaxy Watch 5</a> is our <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">top recommendation</a> in our smartwatch guide. Usually $280, it&#39;s currently $160, which is 43 percent off. Samsung&#39;s latest wearables run on Google&#39;s Wear OS and gives you plenty of health data and fitness tracking along with sleep coaching and body composition analysis.</p><h2> Fitbit Versa 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="9089883eb4874ad2841c444d114365d2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9GaXRiaXQtRml0bmVzcy1TbWFydHdhdGNoLVRyYWNraW5nLUluY2x1ZGVkL2RwL0IwN1RXRlZEV1Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMW9pLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmM1OTJlMS0wNGM1LTRkNWQtODIzZi1mNDM3MWJjNmE0NTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAf1D2MMCTXjqREiUAyEHEcC4AEVPlgDSRjuTrQojPbSi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-Fitness-Smartwatch-Tracking-Included%2Fdp%2FB07TWFVDWT" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit Versa 2</a> is the <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">budget pick</a> in our smartwatch guide and down to $124 for Prime Day. Fitbit devices have always been fitness-focused and the Versa 2 tracks and auto-detects a slew of different workouts giving you plenty of data. But since it&#39;s a smartwatch, it can play Spotify, has Alexa built in and brings your phone notifications and hundreds of apps to your wrist. It&#39;s also device agnostic, pairing up with either iPhones or Android devices.</p><h2> Fitness Trackers</h2><h2> Fitbit Charge 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="3ca3961339a849b186239c6fa3ea758f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCWFE0SE1CP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJjNTkyZTEtMDRjNS00ZDVkLTgyM2YtZjQzNzFiYzZhNDU4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAcii-L339Tpmr7Dfew_VEJk_l6YrBQ5SnnSPgodP4e9W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09BXQ4HMB" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit Charge 5</a> is our <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-fitness-trackers-133053484.html">favorite overall</a> tracker, and is currently $100 or $50 off its usual price. Fitness trackers aren&#39;t as fully featured as smartwatches, but that typically means they have a longer battery life and cost a little less. We like the Charge 5 for its comprehensive activity tracking and health monitoring that comes in a thin profile with a multi-day battery life. It also pairs with both Apple and Android phones.</p><h2> Fitbit Inspire 3 </h2><p><core-commerce id="fa924e40474a4d42ac8e5df74a64302a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Our favorite budget <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-fitness-trackers-133053484.html">fitness tracker</a> is <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaw4c9Vv1eHbynaNB6JKg6ucRLzykwOdDyPjVDz5bjeb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B5F9SZW7%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit&#39;s Inspire 3</a> and Prime Day is making it even more affordable with a 20-percent discount that makes it just $80 rather than $100. It doesn&#39;t have built-in GPS, but if you bring your phone along, its connected GPS capabilities will give you all the same data. It does offer monitoring for your heart rate, blood oxygen and skin temperature variations.</p><p> <strong><em>Your Prime Day Shopping Guide</em></strong> <em>: See all of our</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day</em></a> <em>coverage.</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1"